    AllocateCreditsNewestFirstDistributionStrategy

    public class AllocateCreditsDistributionStrategy
extends DirectBillDistributionStrategy
    Allocate the credits to pay off the positive items. Only use the amount of credit needed to completely pay off the positive items.
